OtherComments.Content: Select Glyphs for Tagging 1) Generate glyphnames from the Tools Menu and give focus to the glyph overview. 2) Edit the list if you want to select more or fewer glyphs. 3) Add a comma or a space as a separator: line breaks are optional. 4) Use quotes for glyph names containing hyphens like "alpha-grek.pcap", 5) Click the Validate button to count the glyphs that will be selected.
